	"name": "Slay",
	"type": "feat",
	"img": "icons/skills/melee/strike-dagger-skull-white.webp",
	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><strong>Bonus Action</strong> - 1 Creature - 2/Short Rest</p><p>Your target must be &amp;reference[bloodied], &amp;reference[incapacitated], &amp;reference[prone], or &amp;reference[restrained].</p><ul><li><p>You make a <strong>single attack</strong> with a weapon. <strong>If you hit</strong>, you can then attack the same target <strong>a second time</strong>.</p></li><li><p>If you reduce a creature to 0 hit points with either attack, you ignore any effect or ability the creature has that would prevent them from reaching 0, such as an orc's @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-ancestry-background.Item.iM3hmD5dtPEsv6UA]{Relentless Endurance} or the <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.3Dpyp708Lxvq4niO]{Death Ward}</em> spell.</p></li></ul>",
			"chat": ""
		},
